

=Description=

Lars Zimmerman:

"Nature is of course a big recycler and inspires our creativity on the matter. And it is of course an important producer of a million things needed by us. How can we make the recycle and (re)creational power of nature visible and get connected to it by using digital media? How can we give nature „digital voices“ to collaborate better with it? 
 
In the workshop we will explore ideas on the subject and also our landscape/biological environment around the place where the workshop takes place! (No coding required. Bring your laptops and cameras if you want.)"
(http://www.larszimmermann.de/site/1ars2imm3rm4nn/natur-digital)


